reviewText: I love watching Usher getting interviewed, he's so real and he's a true artist. I believe he was born to  entertain, he's great at every aspects of it, the stage and business.  this dvd is so interesting, and if your an Usher fan you'll love the old flash back.
I was disappointed.  i was expecting to see a performance from here at this stage in his life.  No music, only interviewed at radio stations.
